{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/Visualization/MapSetting/Projectiongroup/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>地球球体是一个椭球体，而我们研究的地图是一个平面实体。地图投影是这样一个过程，将三维实体转化为二维的平面上来。地图投影定义了转换的一些方法和规则。SuperMap\n提供了三种类型的坐标系统，平面直角坐标系、地理坐标系和投影坐标系。</p>\n<h3 id=\"关于地图投影\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>关于地图投影</h3>\n<p>详细讲述地图投影的过程和地图投影有关概念和原理。</p>\n<h3 id=\"地图投影类型\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>地图投影类型</h3>\n<p>介绍地图投影的类型划分方法，一是按照投影的变形性质分类，二是按照投影的构成方式分类。</p>\n<h3 id=\"常用的地图投影\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 